<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
    <%= image_tag "Hunter4.jpg", width: 250, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

   <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
 <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Welcome to my part of the internet!  </p>
        <p> I'm Hunter Orges (Or-Jess), but my friends call me Hunty, or
        the <em>GOAT</em>. I am fluent in Game of Thrones references, and love
        anything that allows me to unleash my creativity. <p>

        <p> I currently am an instructor of software-development at Dawson Community College,
        and a <mark>freelance developer.</mark> My true love is creating
        solutions to problems with software.

        <p> 
        When I take on a project I give daily updates to ensure that the project is aligning properly with the client's goals. The end result is the right product, delivered on time, and on budget.
        
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn" id="hbutton"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
 <button
            class="btn" id="hbutton"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
           <div class="card card-block">
              Instructor of Software-Development at Dawson Community College
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              College Mentor at Code To Success
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Intern Success in Education
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              UVU
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              SUU
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>